<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>I will be there</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 What happened to my days
 When I was searching
 For someone to love

[V2]
 What happened to my days
 When I was looking for
 Someone to hug

[V3]
 But then you took me by my hands
 You guided me
 And after your sacrifice
 You said to me

[V4]
 I will be there, for you
 Through the sufferance of your days
 I will be there, for you
 And you know I'll always stay
 With all I am I'll give you
 Everything you need
 Remember what I did that day
 For you

[V5]
 I will be there, for you
 Through the sufferance of your days
 I will be there, for you
 And you know I'll always stay

[V6]
 What happened to those days
 The one that I searched for
 Is the one I love</lyrics>
<hymn_number>1802</hymn_number>
<author>Fabio Strippoli</author>
</song>